description: With this photo I hope to have captured a piece of untouched nature, where the sun rays dance on the mountain in the morning as it did hundreds of years ago. Who knows how long it will take these days before humans touch this untouched piece of nature. And should it ever come to that, I hope that this photo will remind you of a time when nature was still untouched.
